<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">10 Best Free AI Image Generators in 2026 (Detailed Comparison)</span></h2>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Microsoft Copilot Designer – Best Free AI Image Generator for Text Rendering</span></h3>
<div id="attachment_201514" style="width: 2570px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-201514" class="wp-image-201514 size-full" src="https://ventureburn.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/Image-from-Microsoft-scaled.jpg" alt="Microsoft Copilot Designer – Best Free AI Image Generator for Text Rendering" width="2560" height="1435" /><p id="caption-attachment-201514" class="wp-caption-text">Image from Microsoft</p></div>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Microsoft Copilot Designer gives you access to DALL-E 3, OpenAI’s most capable image model, completely free. It’s the easiest entry point to DALL-E 3 quality without a ChatGPT Plus subscription, making it one of the most accessible best free AI image generators available. The only cost: a Microsoft account.</span></p>
