<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Adobe Firefly – Best Free AI Image Generator for Commercial Safety</span></h3>
<div id="attachment_201508" style="width: 2570px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-201508" class="wp-image-201508 size-full" src="https://ventureburn.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/Image-from-Adobe-Firefly-scaled.jpg" alt="Adobe Firefly – Best Free AI Image Generator for Commercial Safety" width="2560" height="1435" /><p id="caption-attachment-201508" class="wp-caption-text">Image from Adobe Firefly</p></div>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Adobe Firefly is the only major best free AI image generator trained exclusively on licensed images, Adobe Stock, openly licensed content, and public domain material. Job seekers building portfolios can pair Firefly with the </span><a href="https://ventureburn.com/best-ai-resume-builder/" data-wpel-link="internal"><span style="font-weight: 400;">best AI resume builder</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> to present AI-assisted work professionally.</span></p>
