<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Pros: Full commercial safety, no visible watermark, deeply integrated with Photoshop, strong brand trust</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Cons: 25 credits/month is very low for heavy users, weaker for stylized art, requires an Adobe account</span></li>
</ul>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Canva AI (Magic Media) – Best Basic AI Image Generator for Beginners</span></h3>
